<heading>groups add - Create a group.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  add NAME
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Creates a new group with the given name.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
Examples
</heading>

<pre>
add admins
  Create a group called admins.
</pre>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
list, edit, delete, users, joins
</paragraph>
